ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
PrecisORDER AMENDING SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT (WHITECAP DAKOTA FIRST NATION) which would add to it the name Whitecap Dakota First Nation along with the name of its governing body and a description of the lands where the Whitecap Dakota goods and services tax law would apply.
